	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Mar 11th 1:54 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey guys,<br><br>I am a lvl 3 enchanter and I don't know where to start.<br><br>What should I put my points into?&nbsp;&nbsp;What are the best spells to have?  How can I level up REALLY FAST without having to repedatley kill crappy things?<br><br>Please give me some answers,<br><br>Thanks,<br><br>A lvl 3 Enchanter<br>Altomar of Druzzil Ro<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
